==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Expertness
<hw>Ex*pert"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Skill derived from practice;
readiness; <as>as, <ex>expertness</ex> in seamanship, or in
reasoning</as>.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Facility; readiness; dexterity; adroitness;
skill. See <er>Facility</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expetible</ent>⟦br⟧
